OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1771952662
OL,3,CPost-mortem 'inconclusive' into deaths
OL,4,Cof teenage couple at holiday park
OL,6,FInvestigations into the deaths of two
OL,7,Fteenagers who died at an East
OL,8,FYorkshire holiday park are continuing
OL,9,Fafter an initial post-mortem
OL,10,Fexamination returned an "inconclusive"
OL,11,Fresult, police have confirmed.
OL,13,FEthan Slater, aged 17, and Cherish
OL,14,FBean, aged 15, who were believed to be
OL,15,Ffrom Sheffield, were found dead inside
OL,16,Fa rental property located at Little
OL,17,FEden Holiday Park in Bridlington on
OL,18,FWednesday, 18 February 2026.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1771952662
OL,3,CPost-mortem 'inconclusive' into deaths
OL,4,Cof teenage couple at holiday park
OL,6,FOn Friday, 20 February, police
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the pair are thought to
OL,8,Fhave died from carbon monoxide
OL,9,Fpoisoning. However, in a statement
OL,10,Ftoday, Humberside Police said that
OL,11,Fwhile post-mortem examinations have
OL,12,Ftaken place, they produced an
OL,13,F"inconclusive result" and "further
OL,14,Ftesting is required to determine the
OL,15,Fcause of Cherish and Ethan's death."
OL,17,FThe force added that carbon monoxide
OL,18,Fpoisoning remains its primary line of
OL,19,Finquiry.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1771952662
OL,3,CPost-mortem 'inconclusive' into deaths
OL,4,Cof teenage couple at holiday park
OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer at
OL,7,FHumberside police, Detective Chief
OL,8,FInspector Ben Robinson said: "This
OL,9,Foutcome comes at what is
OL,10,Funderstandably an extremely difficult
OL,11,Ftime for their families, and our
OL,12,Fthoughts remain firmly with them as
OL,13,Fthey continue to grieve the loss of
OL,14,Ftheir loved ones. They are being kept
OL,15,Ffully informed of all developments and
OL,16,Fcontinue to be supported by specialist
OL,17,Ftrained officers."
OL,26,@pD@^OU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1771952662
OL,3,CPost-mortem 'inconclusive' into deaths
OL,4,Cof teenage couple at holiday park
OL,6,FPolice also confirmed that a third
OL,7,Fman, who was arrested on Saturday, 21
OL,8,FFebruary on suspicion of gross
OL,9,Fnegligence manslaughter, has since
OL,10,Fbeen released on bail. Two other men,
OL,11,Faged 33 and 42, also remain on
OL,12,Fconditional bail.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1771952662
OL,3,CPost-mortem 'inconclusive' into deaths
OL,4,Cof teenage couple at holiday park
OL,6,FDCI Robinson added: "I would like to
OL,7,Foffer my reassurance that this update
OL,8,Fdoes not represent the conclusion of
OL,9,Four enquiries and there is significant
OL,10,Fwork progressing simultaneously,
OL,11,Fincluding specialist analysis,
OL,12,Fsearches of the premises, and the
OL,13,Fextensive review of all the
OL,14,Finformation collated in coordination
OL,15,Fwith partner agencies.
OL,26,@nD@UOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1771952662
OL,3,CPost-mortem 'inconclusive' into deaths
OL,4,Cof teenage couple at holiday park
OL,6,F"While the medical cause of death has
OL,7,Fnot yet been formally confirmed,
OL,8,Fcarbon monoxide poisoning remains a
OL,9,Fprimary line of enquiry. We are
OL,10,Fcarefully reviewing and analysing all
OL,11,Fevidence gathered to ensure we
OL,12,Festablish the full circumstances in
OL,13,Fthe lead up to and surrounding these
OL,14,Fdeaths."
OL,16,F"The cordon at the site remains in
OL,17,Fplace while further specialist work is
OL,18,Fundertaken. We continue to work
OL,19,Fclosely with the Health and Safety
OL,20,FExecutive, Humberside Fire & Rescue,
OL,21,Fand East Riding of Yorkshire Council.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
